OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FOil prices soared to more than $100 a
OL,7,Fbarrel - a four-year high - fuelling
OL,8,Fglobal fears of rising inflation as
OL,9,Fthe escalating conflict entered its
OL,10,Fsecond week.
OL,12,FIsrael launched fresh strikes on
OL,13,FTehran overnight, as Iran struck Gulf
OL,14,Fcountries, despite an apology over the
OL,15,Fweekend from the country's president,
OL,16,FMasoud Pezeshkian, for targeting its
OL,17,Fneighbours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
