OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FThe Israeli Air Force hit "a rocket
OL,7,Fengine production facility and several
OL,8,Flong-range ballistic missiles launch
OL,9,Fsites," the Israel Defence Forces said
OL,10,Fin a statement. The Israeli military
OL,11,Falso said it struck Hezbollah
OL,12,Finfrastructure in Lebanon's capital,
OL,13,FBeirut. Videos online also showed a
OL,14,Ffire at Beirut's Ramada hotel and
OL,15,Fdamage to an apartment at the hotel
OL,16,Fafter an Israeli attack.
