OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FDozens were injured in an Iranian
OL,7,Fattack on Monday on Bahrain. Bahrain's
OL,8,Fstate oil company declared force
OL,9,Fmajeure - a legal manoeuvre that
OL,10,Freleases a company from its
OL,11,Fcontractual obligations because of
OL,12,Fextraordinary circumstances - on
OL,13,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
