OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FVideos shared on social media showed a
OL,7,Flarge fire in an industrial zone
OL,8,Fhousing the national oil company,
OL,9,FBAPCO. It said the company's
OL,10,Foperations "have been affected by the
OL,11,Fongoing regional conflict in the
OL,12,FMiddle East and the recent attack on
OL,13,Fits refinery complex", but insisted
OL,14,Flocal demand could be met.
OL,16,FAt least 32 people, including
OL,17,Fchildren, were injured in Iranian
OL,18,Fdrone strikes on the town of Sitra,
OL,19,Fabout six kilometres (nearly 4 miles)
OL,20,Ffrom the industrial area.
