OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FThere were also reports of blasts in
OL,7,FAbu Dhabi, while Saudi Arabia, Qatar
OL,8,Fand Kuwait said they had intercepted
OL,9,Fdrones and missiles.
OL,11,FHuge plumes of black smoke engulfed
OL,12,FTehran on Saturday after several oil
OL,13,Frefineries were targeted. Iranians
OL,14,Fhave been advised to wear masks and to
OL,15,Favoid turning on air conditioners or
OL,16,Fgoing outside immediately after
OL,17,Frainfall.
OL,19,FOil prices continue to soar
