OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FOil prices have skyrocketed to around
OL,7,F$114 (#85.50) a barrel due to the
OL,8,Fongoing conflict, causing Asian
OL,9,Fmarkets to plunge early on Monday.
OL,11,FConcerns regarding its impact on UK
OL,12,Fhouseholds' bills remain, as energy
OL,13,Fbills are forecast to rise by 10% from
OL,14,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
