OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FRegarding the rising oil prices, US
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump posted on
OL,8,Fsocial media that "Short term oil
OL,9,Fprices, which will drop rapidly when
OL,10,Fthe destruction of the Iran nuclear
OL,11,Fthreat is over, is a very small price
OL,12,Fto pay for U.S.A., and World, Safety
OL,13,Fand Peace. ONLY FOOLS WOULD THINK
OL,14,FDIFFERENTLY!
OL,16,FIsraeli Military claims strikes on
OL,17,FIsfahan
