OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FIsrael has warned of new incoming
OL,7,Fmissile fire from Iran. Moments later,
OL,8,Fsirens sounded in parts of northern
OL,9,FIsrael.
OL,11,FAt least 1,205 civilians have been
OL,12,Fkilled in Iran since the conflict
OL,13,Fbegan, according to the US-based Human
OL,14,FRights Activists News Agency (HRANA).
OL,15,FThe total, which includes 194
OL,16,Fchildren, is as of 5 pm ET on
OL,17,FSaturday, HRANA said.
