OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FIran's Assembly of Experts named
OL,7,FMojtaba Khamenei to succeed his
OL,8,Ffather, Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, as the
OL,9,Fcountry's new supreme leader,
OL,10,Faccording to state media.
OL,12,FAli Khamenei was killed in US-Israeli
OL,13,Fstrikes last weekend.
OL,15,FMojtaba Khamenei, 56, was not
OL,16,Fimmediately announced on Sunday, after
OL,17,FIsrael and the US threatened to target
OL,18,Fany successor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
