OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FPresident Trump had earlier told ABC
OL,7,FNews he wants a say in who comes to
OL,8,Fpower once the war is over. A new
OL,9,Fleader "is not going to last long"
OL,10,Fwithout his approval, Trump added.
OL,12,FLebanon death toll rises to nearly 400
OL,14,FIsrael's military launched new strikes
OL,15,Fon Lebanon on Sunday, declaring that
OL,16,Fit was targeting commanders of the
OL,17,FLebanon branch of Iran's Revolutionary
OL,18,FGuards' Quds Force.
