OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FLebanon's health minister said that 83
OL,7,Fchildren are among the 394 killed so
OL,8,Ffar in the latest round of conflict,
OL,9,Fwhich has seen fighting resume between
OL,10,FIsrael and Hezbollah militants.
OL,12,FMore than 100,000 people in Lebanon
OL,13,Fhave been forced to seek shelter, the
OL,14,FUnited Nations World Food Programme
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FStarmer speaks to Trump
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
