OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer spoke with President
OL,7,FTrump on Sunday afternoon, after the
OL,8,FUS president spent the weekend hitting
OL,9,Fout at the prime minister.
OL,11,FThe UK initially would not let the US
OL,12,Fuse its military bases to facilitate
OL,13,Fstrikes on Iran, but later agreed to
OL,14,Fallow their use for "specific
OL,15,Fdefensive operations", with the US
OL,16,Fsending bomber planes to RAF Fairford
OL,17,Fin Gloucestershire this weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
