CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773065473
OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FPreparations have been made to send
OL,7,Faircraft carrier HMS Prince of Wales
OL,8,Fto the Middle East region, and while
OL,9,Fno decisions have been made, Trump did
OL,10,Fnot appear impressed by the offer.
OL,12,FIn a post on his Truth Social platform
OL,13,Fon Saturday, the US president wrote:
OL,14,F"The United Kingdom, our once Great
OL,15,FAlly, maybe the Greatest of them all,
OL,16,Fis finally giving serious thought to
OL,17,Fsending two aircraft carriers to the
OL,18,FMiddle East.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
