SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773065473
OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,F"That's OK, Prime Minister Starmer, we
OL,7,Fdon't need them any longer ` But we
OL,8,Fwill remember. We don't need people
OL,9,Fthat join Wars after we've already
OL,10,Fwon!"
OL,12,FRegarding the conversation between the
OL,13,Ftwo leaders, a Downing Street
OL,14,Fspokeswoman said: "The leaders began
OL,15,Fby discussing the latest situation in
OL,16,Fthe Middle East and the military co-
OL,17,Foperation between the UK and US
OL,18,Fthrough the use of RAF bases in
OL,19,Fsupport of the collective self-defence
OL,20,Fof partners in the region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@EO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
