OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773065473
OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,F"The Prime Minister also shared his
OL,7,Fheartfelt condolences with President
OL,8,FTrump and the American people
OL,9,Ffollowing the deaths of six US
OL,10,Fsoldiers."
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,13,Fdefended Starmer on Sunday, saying he
OL,14,Fis "right to stand up for Britain and
OL,15,FBritain's interests" and that the UK
OL,16,Fneeds to "take decisions ourselves".
OL,18,FHow did we get here?
