OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FJust over one week ago, Israel and the
OL,7,FUS launched what they described as
OL,8,F"pre-emptive" strikes against Iran,
OL,9,Fwhich they view as intent on acquiring
OL,10,Fnuclear weapons, shortly after a round
OL,11,Fof negotiations.
OL,13,FIran denies seeking nuclear weapons,
OL,14,Fand some legal experts have said the
OL,15,Fattack violated international law. The
OL,16,FIslamic Republic has responded by
OL,17,Fstriking Israel and a number of
OL,18,Ftargets in Gulf states allied with the
OL,19,FUS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
