PN,30420
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773065473
OL,3,COil prices soar to four-year high as
OL,4,CKhamenei's son named Iran's new leader
OL,6,FThe war's stated goals and timelines
OL,7,Fhave repeatedly shifted as the US has
OL,8,Fat times suggested it seeks to topple
OL,9,FIran's government or elevate new
OL,10,Fleadership.
OL,12,FWhile US President Donald Trump
OL,13,Fpreviously dismissed the idea of boots
OL,14,Fon the ground in Iran, he did not rule
OL,15,Fit out when asked on Saturday.
OL,17,FHe said US troops could "possibly" be
OL,18,Fsent on the ground in Iran, as the war
OL,19,Fcontinues, but there would have to be
OL,20,Fa "very good reason".
